          "@type": "Question",
          name: "Can I use Stocky Swap with multiple Shopify stores?",
          acceptedAnswer: { "@type": "Answer", text: "Yes. Each Shopify store needs its own Make.com webhook connection, but the Stocky Swap scenario can be cloned and configured separately per store. Multi-store operators typically point each store's webhook to a separate tab or sheet within one master Google Sheets workbook for unified reporting. Note that Make.com free tier operations are counted across all your scenarios — high multi-store volume may require upgrading to Make.com Core." }
        }
      ]
